hopobject.body: Could I have a statement, please? anavar dose female It was bound to be a challenge, because Siegfried is not much given to sublimity. There’s an awful lot of sinister tuba and dark string tremolandos, accompanying the vengeful broodings of various dwarfs. There’s comedy, when Siegfried drives in a bear and scares Mime out of his wits (not seen in this modest “semi-staging”, alas). There’s a dragon, whom Siegfried kills (somewhere out in the wings on this occasion), there’s a bird who guides him to the sleeping heroine that he will awaken in the final scene.
